success.jsp->findAllArticles.action-->showAllArticles.jsp

添加文章:addArticles.jsp->editbloginfo.jsp->addArticle.action

数据库bloginfo  username,blogTitle,idiograph
login.jsp->login.action->editbloginfo.jsp->editbloginfo.action

==================================主页===================================
用户登陆之后-->showAllArticle.action(显示所有用户的文章)-->showAllArticle.jsp

点击用户首页-->showAllArticle.action(显示所有用户的文章)-->showAllArticle.jsp

点击个性化设置-->editbloginfo.jsp--->editbloginfo.action-->showUserAllArticle.action-->showUserAllArticle.jsp

点击写日志-->addArticle.jsp-->addArticle.action-->showUserAllArticle.jsp

点击相册-->showphoto.action-->showphoto.jsp===> 1.点击浏览

点击留言板-->showMessageBoard.action-->showMessageBoard.jsp